{
  "info": {
    "name": "FlashCart Backend API",
    "_postman_id": "flashcart-backend-collection",
    "description": "Complete API collection for the FlashCart hyperlocal delivery backend.\n\n**Setup:**\n1. Import this collection into Postman.\n2. Create a new Environment with these variables (all empty to start):\n   - `BASE_URL` = `http://localhost:5000/api/v1`\n   - `TOKEN` (user access token — auto-set by login)\n   - `ADMIN_TOKEN` (admin access token — auto-set by admin login)\n   - `RIDER_TOKEN` (rider access token — auto-set by rider login)\n   - `CATEGORY_ID`, `STORE_ID`, `PRODUCT_ID`, `ADDRESS_ID`, `ORDER_ID`, `RIDER_ID`\n\n**Test Order:** Auth → Admin Setup → Products → Cart → Checkout → Rider → Admin Orders",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Auth (User)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Test User\",\n  \"contactNumber\": \"9876543210\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass1\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{BASE_URL}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "register"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.data && res.data.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.environment.set('TOKEN', res.data.accessToken);",
                  "  console.log('USER TOKEN saved');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"contactNumber\": \"9876543210\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass1\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{BASE_URL}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Admin Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.data && res.data.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.environment.set('ADMIN_TOKEN', res.data.accessToken);",
                  "  console.log('ADMIN TOKEN saved');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"contactNumber\": \"9999999999\",\n  \"password\": \"AdminPass1\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{BASE_URL}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get My Sessions",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{TOKEN}}"}],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/auth/sessions",
              "host": ["{{BASE_URL}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "sessions"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"PASTE_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/auth/refresh-token",
              "host": ["{{BASE_URL}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "refresh-token"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{TOKEN}}"}],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/auth/logout",
              "host": ["{{BASE_URL}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "logout"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout All Sessions",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{TOKEN}}"}],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/auth/sessions",
              "host": ["{{BASE_URL}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "sessions"]
